mods.abstract: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Jack Greene, Jeannie Seely, the Jolly Giants, Jimmy Dry, Bill Carlisles and the Carlisles and Claude King at the North Armory on July 28. Poster features metal photoplates of Jack Greene, Jeannie Seely, the Jolly Giants, Jimmy Dry, Bill Carlisles and Claude King.
